{"tid":342391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"旅遊達人項明生涉非禮大學男生被捕","createTime":"2017-07-31T14:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T14:58:25.000Z","uid":25021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d8363bc45b1de9c3d29d01372a82a1bee0c0abe2","tid":342391,"uid":25021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:33:24.000Z","msg":"著名旅遊達人項明生（James）涉嫌非禮男子被警方拘捕。消息稱，一名大學生上周三(26日)報案稱，他於前一天在北角英皇道一間寫字樓見工時<strong>被人強吻及摸下體</strong>，警方接報調查後，今午拘捕47歲的項明生，通宵扣查。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，一名22歲大學男生較早前在書展認識項明生，其後更獲安排工作機會，大學生於上周二(25日)到北角英皇道一工業大廈見工，<strong>其間有人表現非常熱情，做出過份動作，令他感到尷尬及不安</strong>，大學生翌日報警求助，聲稱見工時，<strong>在不自願下被一名男子強吻、摸下體等</strong>。警方接報展開調查後，於今午5時許，在北角英皇道一單位內，拘捕47歲的項明生，案件暫列非禮男子案，交東區刑事偵查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》晚上就事件致電項明生查詢，惟其手機一直無人接聽。<br />\n<br />\n項明生是旅遊達人、旅遊節目主持、專欄作家，近年活躍於跨媒體工作。項明生1969年在四川成都出世，16歲時移居香港，半工讀於1989年考入香港大學文學院主修日本研究及心理學，及後於1996年在香港中文大學取得工商管理碩士。1997年加入Sony Computer Entertainment Hong Kong Limited，於2013年成為智傲集團行政總裁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170731&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57025641\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170731%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57025641&d=hE3THAwR%2BRpaIiUHAoFHfYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=080e331f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170731%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57025641&h=fda60d02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170731&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57025641</a><br />\n旅遊達人項明生涉非禮大學男生被捕"},{"pid":"a0e4262bbcb49df932cbf8a1ee73d69b5ec894f9","tid":342391,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3513281ee7181b7c120ec56a3c7211fb7e9ba374","tid":342391,"uid":118700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:57:09.000Z","msg":"見工都要比人摸J<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cec5b3368c28c5a4df32f85382fa4b1d38a533","tid":342391,"uid":118700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:57:09.000Z","msg":"見工都要比人摸J<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f0f227d84a87876bd11214e23b15050331a7b6","tid":342391,"uid":55327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:58:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}